Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: This individual was a member of the One Sith. After the death of Darth Krayt, he complied with his superiors and proceeded to infiltrate the upper echelons of the new Galactic Triumvirate; infiltrating the legion on Ceitia Five. He, however, was flushed out in 138 ABY by Darth Wredd and killed, the latter initiating his own plans for the Sith.
